A_n=\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{(-1)^k}{k}
(A_n)_n
(A_{2n})_n
(A_{2n+1})_n
A_{2n+1}-A_{2n}\to 0
A_{2n+1}-A_{2n} = -\frac{1}{2n+1}
\frac{1}{2k(2k+1)}\operatorname*{\sim}_{k\to\infty}\frac{1}{4k^2}
 A_{2n+1} = -1 + \sum_{k=1}^n \left( \frac{1}{2k} - \frac{1}{2k+1}\right) = -1 + \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{1}{2k(2k+1)} 
